# File Organization

Compiled from C2DS-brood, C2DS-bootstrap, gecl-app-common, dot_shellrc, c2ds_mobile_provisioning_app AGENTS.md.

## Markdown Files

**Rule:** All `.md` files belong in `docs/` directory.

**Exceptions (stay in root only):**

- `README.md` - Project overview
- `AGENTS.md` - AI agent instructions

**Place in docs/:**

- Design docs, guides, standards
- Implementation notes
- Architecture documentation
- Coding standards

## AI Rules

- If project uses `.ai-rules/` - keep rules there
- If project uses `.cursor/rules/` - keep rules there

## Scripts

- Keep in `scripts/`, `tools/`, or `bin/` directory
